This is Bunmi's cart Commit
As a user, I want to be able to add products to my cart so that I can purchase products with ease

REQUIREMENT
1. User should be able to launch the URL jumia.com.ng
2. User should be able to add products from different categories to cart
3. User should be able to click start shopping button from cart to take them to home page where items will be added to cart when cart is empty
4. User should be able to remove items, increase quantity or reduce quantity from the cart
5. User should be able to checkout after making all modifications to the products in the cart
